Largo Winch (001 - 015) (1991 - 2014) (DCP-Novus-Empire)


Largo Winczlav is a yugoslavian orphan, adopted in secret by Nerio Winch to lead his business empire when he dies.
After the murder of his adopted father the young orphan is propelled to the head of the Group W, Nerios' business empire and becomes one of the most wealthy people in the world overnight
